{"tid":1624323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"104各區手足要做的3件事","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T03:50:08.000Z","uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"207a727a81a628145ebe079c8579f610c467cb64","tid":1624323,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 消防被大量藍絲施壓</span><br />\n記得佢哋 係呢個運動裏面幫助咗我哋好多<br />\n請到每區消防局表達感謝 <span style=\"color: red;\">放紅玫瑰在消防局門口， 真心嘅感謝信攝在消防閘下面</span>，希望前線消防睇到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 太多人唔明白 點解要破壞360同美心</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">set 街站向市民解釋清楚</span>， 有啲人係唔會睇到連儂牆， 但你講畀佢哋聽 佢哋係會理解<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 唔好畀人屈係賊</span><br />\n除360, 美心， 黨鐵及政務大樓，其他舖頭請不要再裝修 ， 唔好 令市民誤會我哋走去偷嘅 ， 同埋表達到我哋識收識放<br />\n<br />\n感謝消防(要前線消防企我哋呢邊) tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OoVlEBVOjoh-p4QyZUr3kw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOoVlEBVOjoh-p4QyZUr3kw&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqlYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=9ab879a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OoVlEBVOjoh-p4QyZUr3kw</a>"},{"pid":"145ec116045a86c84e45ea3dee1410947dfad799","tid":1624323,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"e044f251cd5da05727e6f8fd72532e350d95cf66","tid":1624323,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:34:05.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"c91d009b7107983a78640739091f330eb1b0091c","tid":1624323,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:34:17.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"63871d814ce5a4a144b7cd3af5d2774c295194ce","tid":1624323,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:34:27.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"9425d6d7fd670d175a220141feab07e2b53488a9","tid":1624323,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20